-- Hugh Osmond May Bid for Dubai International's  Alliance Medical, Sky Says
-- B y   A l e x   M o r a l e s
-- 2010-10-02T14:38:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-02/hugh-osmond-may-bid-for-dubai-international-s-alliance-medical-sky-says.html
Pizza Express founder  Hugh Osmond  is
interested in buying medical services company Alliance Medical,
Sky News Business Editor  Mark Kleinman  wrote today in a  blog  on
the television station’s website.  Osmond’s Horizon Acquisition Co. is among a group of
bidders who have expressed interest in Alliance Medical, which
has been put up for sale by Dubai International Capital,
Kleinman wrote, without saying where he got the information.  Anthony Carlisle , an external spokesman for Horizon with
Citigate Dewe Rogerson, declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Alex Morales  in London at 
 amorales2@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Reed Landberg at   landberg@bloomberg.net . 